introduce yourself. Tell us a little bit about your role, the organization, and maybe

00:02:38.539 --> 00:02:40.860
something you do in your free time outside of work.

00:02:41.619 --> 00:02:46.500
Sure. Thank you, Rachel, for the kind introduction and for the congratulations. Yeah,

