mention it, but I appreciate you noticing and bringing it up. So I am Patrick Tennant.

00:02:57.899 --> 00:03:01.740
As Rachel said, the Senior Director of Data Science and Analytics for the Meadows Mental

00:03:01.740 --> 00:03:06.860
Health Policy Institute. And let me read the mission statement of the Institute because

00:03:07.100 --> 00:03:12.779
the bosses will want me to get this one right. So the Meadows Mental Health Policy

00:03:12.779 --> 00:03:17.860
Institute provides independent, nonpartisan, data-driven, and trusted policy and program

